{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/privacy/layout,_N_T_/privacy/page,_N_T_/privacy"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--Pi3QqkS_HDMn2ae5bDKfc--><html lang=\"en\" class=\"__variable_188b3f __variable_8b3a0b __variable_6d24ac\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/a4546f67ddbda619.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-05173f67f96f24be.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-c023c6e3521b1417.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/255-3981a3d1f3561bd8.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-3d02345fdecf95ee.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/297-acf454feea2a9bd2.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/144-c47888c54fecf75a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-110608b261c61e80.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://upload-widget.cloudinary.com/global/all.js\" as=\"script\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://accounts.google.com/gsi/client\" as=\"script\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"180x180\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"32x32\" href=\"/favicon-32x32.png\"/><link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"16x16\" href=\"/favicon-16x16.png\"/><link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/site.webmanifest\"/><title>Privacy Policy — OPINIONPLUS</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"A platform to tell your story, with your name and logo at the top, and the tools to build an audience around your truth.\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"font-body bg-paper text-ink min-h-screen flex flex-col antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"border-b border-wire bg-paper/95 backdrop-blur sticky top-0 z-40\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between h-16\"><a class=\"flex items-baseline gap-2 group\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"editorial-h text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight\">OPINION<span class=\"text-signal\">PLUS</span></span><span class=\"hidden sm:inline wire-tag\">every voice, a masthead</span></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium\"><a class=\"hover:text-signal transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Feed</a><a class=\"btn-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-sm\" href=\"/login\">Sign in</a></nav><button class=\"md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-16\"><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">Legal</p><h1 class=\"editorial-h text-4xl font-bold mb-8\">Privacy Policy</h1><p class=\"text-xs text-ink-400 mb-10\">Last updated: July 2026</p><div class=\"prose-story text-ink-700\"><h2 class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\">What we collect</h2><p>When you sign in with Google, we receive your name, email address, and profile photo. When you publish, we store the content you write and any media or files you attach. When you engage with a story — a like, a comment, a rating, a follow — we store that action against your account so it can be shown to other readers.</p><h2 class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\">What we don&#x27;t collect</h2><p>We don&#x27;t require a password, and we don&#x27;t ask for information beyond what publishing and engaging with the platform requires. Unregistered visitors can read and share without an account.</p><h2 class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\">Your rights (GDPR &amp; equivalent)</h2><p>If you&#x27;re in the EU, UK, or a jurisdiction with equivalent protections, you have the right to access, correct, export, or delete your personal data. You can edit your profile directly, or contact us to request a full export or deletion of your account and content.</p><h2 class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\">How long we keep it</h2><p>Your content stays published until you delete it or your account is removed. Admin action logs (moderation actions, IP address at time of action) are retained for platform integrity and are not visible to the public.</p><h2 class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\">Third parties</h2><p>Images and video are processed and delivered by Cloudinary. Documents are stored on Cloudflare R2. Authentication is handled by Google. None of these providers see the content of your stories beyond what&#x27;s necessary to host or display them.</p><h2 class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\">Contact</h2><p>Questions about this policy or a data request can be sent through our<!-- --> <a href=\"/contact\" class=\"text-signal underline\">contact page</a>.</p></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-wire mt-24\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-12 grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div><p class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-extrabold\">OPINION<span class=\"text-signal\">PLUS</span></p><p class=\"text-sm text-ink-400 mt-2 max-w-xs\">A platform where every person gets a masthead — their name, their logo, their truth, at the top of the page.</p></div><div><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">Read</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/\">Feed</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/about\">About OpinionPlus</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">Legal &amp; support</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy policy</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"rule\"><p class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-5 text-xs text-ink-400\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> OpinionPlus. Every byline belongs to the person who wrote it.</p></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-05173f67f96f24be.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7768,[\\\"297\\\",\\\"static/chunks/297-acf454feea2a9bd2.js\\\",\\\"144\\\",\\\"static/chunks/144-c47888c54fecf75a.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-110608b261c61e80.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[6128,[\\\"297\\\",\\\"static/chunks/297-acf454feea2a9bd2.js\\\",\\\"144\\\",\\\"static/chunks/144-c47888c54fecf75a.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-110608b261c61e80.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[9766,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[8924,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:I[2619,[\\\"297\\\",\\\"static/chunks/297-acf454feea2a9bd2.js\\\",\\\"144\\\",\\\"static/chunks/144-c47888c54fecf75a.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-110608b261c61e80.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n14:I[7150,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/a4546f67ddbda619.css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"0:{\\\"P\\\":null,\\\"b\\\":\\\"Pi3QqkS-HDMn2ae5bDKfc\\\",\\\"p\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"c\\\":[\\\"\\\",\\\"privacy\\\"],\\\"i\\\":false,\\\"f\\\":[[[\\\"\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"privacy\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"__PAGE__\\\",{}]}]},\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",true],[\\\"\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$1\\\",\\\"c\\\",{\\\"children\\\":[[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"link\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"rel\\\":\\\"stylesheet\\\",\\\"href\\\":\\\"/_next/static/css/a4546f67ddbda619.css\\\",\\\"precedence\\\":\\\"next\\\",\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"nonce\\\":\\\