g, a follow — we store that action against your account so it can be shown to other readers.\"}]\n8:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\",\"children\":\"What we don't collect\"}]\n9:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We don't require a password, and we don't ask for information beyond what publishing and engaging with the platform requires. Unregistered visitors can read and share without an account.\"}]\na:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\",\"children\":\"Your rights (GDPR & equivalent)\"}]\nb:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"If you're in the EU, UK, or a jurisdiction with equivalent protections, you have the right to access, correct, export, or delete your personal data. You can edit your profile directly, or contact us to request a full export or deletion of your account and content.\"}]\nc:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\",\"children\":\"How long we keep it\"}]\nd:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Your content stays published until you delete it or your account is removed. Admin action logs (moderation actions, IP address at time of action) are retained for platform integrity and are not visible to the public.\"}]\ne:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\",\"children\":\"Third parties\"}]\nf:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"Images and video are processed and delivered by Cloudinary. Documents are stored on Cloudflare R2. Authentication is handled by Google. None of these providers see the content of your stories beyond what's necessary to host or display them.\"}]\n10:[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"editorial-h text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-2\",\"children\":\"Contact\"}]\n11:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":[\"Questions about this policy or a data request can be sent through our\",\" \",[\"$\",\"a\",null,{\"href\":\"/contact\",\"className\":\"text-signal underline\",\"children\":\"contact page\"}],\".\"]}]\n12:[\"$\",\"$L15\",null,{\"children\":[\"$L16\",[\"$\",\"$L17\",null,{\"promise\":\"$@18\"}]]}]\n13:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[[\"$\",\"$L19\",null,{\"children\":\"$L1a\"}],null],[\"$\",\"$L1b\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$1c\",null,{\"fallback\":null,\"children\":\"$L1d\"}]}]}]]}]\n1a:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n16:null\n18:{\"metadata\":[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Privacy Policy — OPINIONPLUS\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"A platform to tell your story, with your name and logo at the top, and the tools to build an audience around your truth.\"}]],\"error\":null,\"digest\":\"$undefined\"}\n1d:\"$18:metadata\"\n"}